{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8",
    "translationId": "dra",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 8,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 8 in Douay-Rheims Bible (Challoner)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.1",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:1",
      "text": "Now Benjamin begot Bale his firstborn, Asbel the second, Ahara the third,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.2",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:2",
      "text": "Nohaa the fourth, and Rapha the fifth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.3",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:3",
      "text": "And the sons of Bale were Addar, and Gera, and Abiud,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.4",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:4",
      "text": "And Abisue, and Naaman, and Ahoe,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.5",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:5",
      "text": "And Gera, and Sephuphan, and Huram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.6",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:6",
      "text": "These are the sons of Abed, heads of families that dwelt in Gabaa, who were removed into Manahath.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.7",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:7",
      "text": "And Naaman, and Achia, and Gera he removed them, and begot Oza, and Ahiud.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.8",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:8",
      "text": "And Saharim begot in the land of Moab, after he sent away Husim and Bara his wives.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.9",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:9",
      "text": "And he begot of Hodes his wife Jobab, and Sebia, and Mosa, and Molchom,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.10",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:10",
      "text": "And Jehus and Sechia, and Marma. These were his sons heads of their families.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.11",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:11",
      "text": "And Mehusim begot Abitob, and Elphaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.12",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:12",
      "text": "And the sons of Elphaal were Heber, and Misaam, and Samad: who built Ono, and Lod, and its daughters.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.13",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:13",
      "text": "And Baria, and Sama were heads of their kindreds that dwelt in Aialon: these drove away the inhabitants of Geth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.14",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:14",
      "text": "And Ahio, and Sesac, and Jerimoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.15",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:15",
      "text": "And Zabadia, and Arod, and Heder,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.16",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:16",
      "text": "And Michael, and Jespha, and Joha, the sons of Baria.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.17",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:17",
      "text": "And Zabadia, and Mosollam, Hezeci, and Heber,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.18",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:18",
      "text": "And Jesamari, and Jezlia, and Jobab, sons of Elphaal,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.19",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:19",
      "text": "And Jacim, and Zechri, and Zabdi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.20",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:20",
      "text": "And Elioenai, and Selethai, and Elial,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.21",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:21",
      "text": "And Adaia, and Baraia, and Samareth, the sons of Semei.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.22",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:22",
      "text": "And Jespham, and Heber, and Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.23",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:23",
      "text": "And Abdon, and Zechri, and Hanan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.24",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:24",
      "text": "And Hanania, and Elam, and Anathothia.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.25",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:25",
      "text": "And Jephdaia, and Phanuel the sons of Sesac.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.26",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:26",
      "text": "And Samsari, and Sohoria and Otholia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.27",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:27",
      "text": "And Jersia, and Elia, and Zechri, the sons of Jeroham.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.28",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:28",
      "text": "These were the chief fathers, and heads of their families who dwelt in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.29",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:29",
      "text": "And at Gabaon dwelt Abigabaon, and the name of his wife was Maacha:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.30",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:30",
      "text": "And his firstborn son Abdon, and Sur, and Cis, and Baal, and Nadab,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.31",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:31",
      "text": "And Gedor, and Ahio, and Zacher, and Macelloth:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.32",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:32",
      "text": "And Macelloth begot Samaa: and they dwelt over against their brethren in Jerusalem with their brethren.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.33",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:33",
      "text": "And Ner begot Cis and Cis begot Saul. And Saul begot Jonathan and Melchisua, and Abinadab, and Esbaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.34",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:34",
      "text": "And the son of Jonathan was Meribbaal: and Meribbaal begot Micha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.35",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:35",
      "text": "And the sons of Micha were Phithon, and Melech, and Tharaa, and Ahaz.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.36",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:36",
      "text": "And Ahaz begot Joada: and Joada begot Alamath, and Azmoth, and Zamri: and Zamri begot Mosa,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.37",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:37",
      "text": "And Mosa begot Banaa, whose son was Rapha, of whom was born Elasa, who begot Asel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.38",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:38",
      "text": "And Asel had six sons whose names were Ezricam, Bochru, Ismahel, Saris, Obdia, and Hanan. All these were the sons of Asel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.39",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:39",
      "text": "And the sons of Esec, his brother, were Ulam the firstborn, and Jehus the second, and Eliphalet the third.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.8.40",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:40",
      "text": "And the sons of Ulam were most valiant men, and archers of great strength: and they had many sons and grandsons, even to a hundred and fifty. All these were children of Benjamin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
